node.text:
Follow these steps👇🏻
1. Introduce yourself in comment section.
-
2. Reply few random comments and say Hi, I am looking for friends to talk in English.
-
3. Start your conversation and if the next person is interested you can talk in DMs.
-
4. Make sure about your purpose of talking, so no flirt or hate speech are allowed.
-
5. If anyone uses offensive language or break the rules of this community just let me know I’ll block them.
-
——————————————
Credit @englishgate4u
